{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Create a horizontal product carousel section for a luxury high-end women's fashion
    brand, inspired by Aro Kai and Self-Portrait — clean, minimal, lots of whitespace.
    
    DATA SOURCE: pull products from a Shopify collection the merchant selects (and also
    allow an optional manual product-picker list as an alternative). Use real product
    data so each card automatically shows the product's image, title, and price, and
    links to that product's page. Prices display in the store currency (GBP).
    
    CARD: each product card = product image on top, then product title, then price
    underneath (like the reference). Keep typography clean and use the theme's existing
    fonts and colors. Default image ratio portrait (3:4), adjustable. Optional: show the
    product's SECOND image on hover (fade) for a premium feel. Let the merchant choose
    whether the card uses the product's featured image or its first gallery image as the
    main image.
    
    INTERACTION: a single horizontal row that the user can:
    - drag/grab to scroll with the mouse ("scroll with hand"),
    - swipe on touch/mobile,
    - and move with prev/next circular arrows (white circle, thin chevron — small and
      elegant, like the reference).
    Clicking a card goes to that product's page.
    
    LAYOUT: show about 3 cards at a time on desktop, 2 on tablet, and 1.5 on mobile
    (so a sliver of the next card peeks in, signalling it scrolls). Generous gap between
    cards. Smooth momentum scrolling.
    
    AESTHETIC: editorial, luxury, neutral — let the products breathe. Optional section
    heading above the row (e.g. "New In" / "Shop The Edit") with size, alignment, and
    uppercase controls.
    
    MOBILE-FIRST: 90% of shoppers are on mobile — the drag/swipe must feel smooth and the
    peek of the next card must be visible.
    
    EDITOR SETTINGS I want: collection picker (and optional manual product list), max
    number of products to show, cards-per-view for desktop/tablet/mobile, card gap,
    image ratio, toggle "show price", toggle "show second image on hover", arrows on/off,
    section top & bottom padding, heading text/size/alignment/uppercase, and background
    color., Refine the product carousel with these changes:
    
    1. MOBILE SWIPE: make the mobile experience a smooth, momentum-based touch swipe
       (like arakii.com) — free-scrolling with a peek of the next card visible, not a
       snap-one-at-a-time slider. It should feel like flicking through a row.
    
    2. CLICK THROUGH IMAGES PER PRODUCT: each product card should let the user browse
       that product's OWN images inside the card, without leaving the page. Tapping/
       clicking the card image (or small left/right zones, or tiny dots) cycles through
       that product's gallery images. The price and title stay visible while cycling.
       Clicking through to the product page still happens via a clear tap on the card /
       title.
    
    3. CHOOSE THE MAIN / COVER IMAGE PER PRODUCT: give the merchant a per-product
       "cover image" override — an image picker on each product entry so we can set the
       first image shown to be ANY image, including ones that are not the product's
       default featured photo. If no override is set, fall back to the product's
       featured image. After the cover, the rest of the product's gallery images follow
       in the click-through.
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% liquid
  if block.settings.collection != blank
    assign products = block.settings.collection.products
  elsif block.settings.product_list != blank
    assign products = block.settings.product_list
  else
    assign products = blank
  endif

  if block.settings.max_products > 0 and products.size > block.settings.max_products
    assign products = products | slice: 0, block.settings.max_products
  endif
%}

{% style %}
  .ai-luxury-carousel-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.background_color }};
    padding-top: {{ block.settings.padding_top }}px;
    padding-bottom: {{ block.settings.padding_bottom }}px;
  }

  .ai-luxury-carousel-container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    max-width: 100%;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 20px;
  }

  .ai-luxury-carousel-header-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    text-align: {{ block.settings.heading_alignment }};
  }

  .ai-luxury-carousel-heading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.heading_size }}px;
    margin: 0;
    color: {{ block.settings.heading_color }};
    {% if block.settings.heading_uppercase %}
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    {% endif %}
  }

  .ai-luxury-carousel-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: relative;
  }

  .ai-luxury-carousel-track-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    gap: {{ block.settings.card_gap }}px;
    overflow-x: auto;
    scroll-behavior: smooth;
    scrollbar-width: none;
    -ms-overflow-style: none;
    cursor: grab;
    user-select: none;
    padding: 4px;
    -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
  }

  .ai-luxury-carousel-track-{{ ai_gen_id }}::-webkit-scrollbar {
    display: none;
  }

  .ai-luxury-carousel-track-{{ ai_gen_id }}.is-dragging {
    cursor: grabbing;
    scroll-behavior: auto;
  }

  .ai-luxury-carousel-card-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    flex: 0 0 calc((100% - ({{ block.settings.cards_mobile | minus: 1 }} * {{ block.settings.card_gap }}px)) / {{ block.settings.cards_mobile }});
    min-width: 0;
  }

  .ai-luxury-carousel-card-content-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: block;
  }

  .ai-luxury-carousel-image-container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: {{ block.settings.image_ratio }};
    overflow: hidden;
    background-color: #f5f5f5;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .ai-luxury-carousel-image-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
    transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
  }

  .ai-luxury-carousel-image-{{ ai_gen_id }}.hidden {
    opacity: 0;
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
  }

  .ai-luxury-carousel-nav-zones-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    display: flex;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .ai-luxury-carousel-nav-zone-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    flex: 1;
    cursor: pointer;
    background: transparent;
    border: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .ai-luxury-carousel-dots-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 12px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    display: flex;
    gap: 6px;
    z-index: 2;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .ai-luxury-carousel-dot-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
    transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .ai-luxury-carousel-dot-{{ ai_gen_id }}.active {
    background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
  }

  .ai-luxury-carousel-card-link-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: block;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .ai-luxury-carousel-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: 14px;
    margin: 0 0 8px;
    color: {{ block.settings.text_color }};
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .ai-luxury-carousel-price-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: {{ block.settings.text_color }};
    margin: 0;
  }

  .ai-luxury-carousel-price-{{ ai_gen_id }} .price__sale {
    color: {{ block.settings.sale_price_color }};
  }

  .ai-luxury-carousel-price-{{ ai_gen_id }} .price__regular {
    text-decoration: line-through;
    opacity: 0.6;
    margin-left: 8px;
  }

  {% if block.settings.show_arrows %}
    .ai-luxury-carousel-nav-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      position: absolute;
      top: calc({{ block.settings.image_ratio | split: '/' | first | times: 100.0 | divided_by: block.settings.image_ratio | split: '/' | last }} / 2);
      transform: translateY(-50%);
      width: 40px;
      height: 40px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
      border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      z-index: 2;
    }

    .ai-luxury-carousel-nav-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
      background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 1);
      border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    }

    .ai-luxury-carousel-nav-prev-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      left: 10px;
    }

    .ai-luxury-carousel-nav-next-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      right: 10px;
    }

    .ai-luxury-carousel-nav-{{ ai_gen_id }} svg {
      width: 16px;
      height: 16px;
      stroke: #000;
      stroke-width: 1.5;
    }
  {% endif %}

  .ai-luxury-carousel-empty-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 60px 20px;
    color: #999;
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  @media screen and (min-width: 750px) {
    .ai-luxury-carousel-card-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      flex: 0 0 calc((100% - ({{ block.settings.cards_tablet | minus: 1 }} * {{ block.settings.card_gap }}px)) / {{ block.settings.cards_tablet }});
    }

    .ai-luxury-carousel-container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: 0 40px;
    }
  }

  @media screen and (min-width: 990px) {
    .ai-luxury-carousel-card-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      flex: 0 0 calc((100% - ({{ block.settings.cards_desktop | minus: 1 }} * {{ block.settings.card_gap }}px)) / {{ block.settings.cards_desktop }});
    }

    .ai-luxury-carousel-container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: 0 60px;
    }
  }
{% endstyle %}

<luxury-product-carousel-{{ ai_gen_id }} class="ai-luxury-carousel-{{ ai_gen_id }}" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
  <div class="ai-luxury-carousel-container-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
    {% if block.settings.heading != blank %}
      <div class="ai-luxury-carousel-header-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        <h2 class="ai-luxury-carousel-heading-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.heading }}</h2>
      </div>
    {% endif %}

    {% if products.size > 0 %}
      <div class="ai-luxury-carousel-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        {% if block.settings.show_arrows %}
          <button class="ai-luxury-carousel-nav-{{ ai_gen_id }} ai-luxury-carousel-nav-prev-{{ ai_gen_id }}" aria-label="Previous products">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
              <polyline points="15 18 9 12 15 6"></polyline>
            </svg>
          </button>
          <button class="ai-luxury-carousel-nav-{{ ai_gen_id }} ai-luxury-carousel-nav-next-{{ ai_gen_id }}" aria-label="Next products">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
              <polyline points="9 18 15 12 9 6"></polyline>
            </svg>
          </button>
        {% endif %}

        <div class="ai-luxury-carousel-track-{{ ai_gen_id }}" data-carousel-track>
          {% for product in products %}
            <div class="ai-luxury-carousel-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}" data-product-card>
              <div class="ai-luxury-carousel-card-content-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                <div class="ai-luxury-carousel-image-container-{{ ai_gen_id }}" data-image-gallery>
                  {% liquid
                    assign product_images = product.images
                    if product_images.size > 0
                      assign all_images = product_images
                    else
                      assign all_images = blank
                    endif
                  %}

                  {% if all_images.size > 0 %}
                    {% for image in all_images %}
                      <img
                        src="{{ image | image_url: width: 800 }}"
                        alt="{{ image.alt | escape }}"
                        loading="lazy"
                        width="{{ image.width }}"
                        height="{{ image.height }}"
                        class="ai-luxury-carousel-image-{{ ai_gen_id }} {% if forloop.index > 1 %}hidden{% endif %}"
                        data-image-index="{{ forloop.index0 }}"
                      >
                    {% endfor %}

                    {% if all_images.size > 1 %}
                      <div class="ai-luxury-carousel-nav-zones-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                        <button class="ai-luxury-carousel-nav-zone-{{ ai_gen_id }}" data-nav-prev aria-label="Previous image"></button>
                        <button class="ai-luxury-carousel-nav-zone-{{ ai_gen_id }}" data-nav-next aria-label="Next image"></button>
                      </div>

                      <div class="ai-luxury-carousel-dots-{{ ai_gen_id }}" data-dots>
                        {% for image in all_images %}
                          <span class="ai-luxury-carousel-dot-{{ ai_gen_id }} {% if forloop.first %}active{% endif %}" data-dot="{{ forloop.index0 }}"></span>
                        {% endfor %}
                      </div>
                    {% endif %}
                  {% else %}
                    <div class="ai-luxury-carousel-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                      {{ 'product-1' | placeholder_svg_tag }}
                    </div>
                  {% endif %}
                </div>

                <a href="{{ product.url }}" class="ai-luxury-carousel-card-link-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                  <h3 class="ai-luxury-carousel-title-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ product.title }}</h3>

                  {% if block.settings.show_price %}
                    <div class="ai-luxury-carousel-price-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                      {% if product.compare_at_price > product.price %}
                        <span class="price__sale">{{ product.price | money }}</span>
                        <span class="price__regular">{{ product.compare_at_price | money }}</span>
                      {% else %}
                        {{ product.price | money }}
                      {% endif %}
                    </div>
                  {% endif %}
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
          {% endfor %}
        </div>
      </div>
    {% else %}
      <div class="ai-luxury-carousel-empty-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        Select a collection or add products to display the carousel
      </div>
    {% endif %}
  </div>
</luxury-product-carousel-{{ ai_gen_id }}>

<script>
  (function() {
    class LuxuryProductCarousel{{ ai_gen_id }} extends HTMLElement {
      constructor() {
        super();
        this.track = null;
        this.prevButton = null;
        this.nextButton = null;
        this.isDragging = false;
        this.startX = 0;
        this.scrollLeft = 0;
        this.velocity = 0;
        this.lastX = 0;
        this.lastTime = 0;
        this.animationFrame = null;
        this.dragThreshold = 5;
        this.totalDragDistance = 0;
      }

      connectedCallback() {
        this.track = this.querySelector('[data-carousel-track]');
        if (!this.track) return;

        this.prevButton = this.querySelector('.ai-luxury-carousel-nav-prev-{{ ai_gen_id }}');
        this.nextButton = this.querySelector('.ai-luxury-carousel-nav-next-{{ ai_gen_id }}');

        this.setupDragScroll();
        this.setupArrowNavigation();
        this.setupImageGalleries();
      }

      setupImageGalleries() {
        const galleries = this.querySelectorAll('[data-image-gallery]');
        
        galleries.forEach(gallery => {
          let currentIndex = 0;
          const images = gallery.querySelectorAll('.ai-luxury-carousel-image-{{ ai_gen_id }}');
          const dots = gallery.querySelectorAll('[data-dot]');
          const prevZone = gallery.querySelector('[data-nav-prev]');
          const nextZone = gallery.querySelector('[data-nav-next]');

          if (images.length <= 1) return;

          const showImage = (index) => {
            images.forEach((img, i) => {
              if (i === index) {
                img.classList.remove('hidden');
              } else {
                img.classList.add('hidden');
              }
            });

            dots.forEach((dot, i) => {
              if (i === index) {
                dot.classList.add('active');
              } else {
                dot.classList.remove('active');
              }
            });

            currentIndex = index;
          };

          if (prevZone) {
            prevZone.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
              e.preventDefault();
              e.stopPropagation();
              const newIndex = currentIndex > 0 ? currentIndex - 1 : images.length - 1;
              showImage(newIndex);
            });
          }

          if (nextZone) {
            nextZone.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
              e.preventDefault();
              e.stopPropagation();
              const newIndex = currentIndex < images.length - 1 ? currentIndex + 1 : 0;
              showImage(newIndex);
            });
          }
        });
      }

      setupDragScroll() {
        this.track.addEventListener('mousedown', this.handleDragStart.bind(this));
        this.track.addEventListener('touchstart', this.handleDragStart.bind(this), { passive: true });
        
        document.addEventListener('mousemove', this.handleDragMove.bind(this));
        document.addEventListener('touchmove', this.handleDragMove.bind(this), { passive: false });
        
        document.addEventListener('mouseup', this.handleDragEnd.bind(this));
        document.addEventListener('touchend', this.handleDragEnd.bind(this));
      }

      setupArrowNavigation() {
        if (this.prevButton) {
          this.prevButton.addEventListener('click', () => {
            const cardWidth = this.track.querySelector('.ai-luxury-carousel-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}').offsetWidth;
            const gap = {{ block.settings.card_gap }};
            this.track.scrollBy({ left: -(cardWidth + gap), behavior: 'smooth' });
          });
        }

        if (this.nextButton) {
          this.nextButton.addEventListener('click', () => {
            const cardWidth = this.track.querySelector('.ai-luxury-carousel-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}').offsetWidth;
            const gap = {{ block.settings.card_gap }};
            this.track.scrollBy({ left: cardWidth + gap, behavior: 'smooth' });
          });
        }
      }

      handleDragStart(e) {
        this.isDragging = true;
        this.totalDragDistance = 0;
        this.track.classList.add('is-dragging');
        
        const touch = e.type === 'touchstart' ? e.touches[0] : e;
        this.startX = touch.pageX - this.track.offsetLeft;
        this.scrollLeft = this.track.scrollLeft;
        this.lastX = touch.pageX;
        this.lastTime = Date.now();
        this.velocity = 0;

        if (this.animationFrame) {
          cancelAnimationFrame(this.animationFrame);
        }
      }

      handleDragMove(e) {
        if (!this.isDragging) return;

        const touch = e.type === 'touchmove' ? e.touches[0] : e;
        const x = touch.pageX - this.track.offsetLeft;
        const walk = (x - this.startX) * 1.5;
        
        this.totalDragDistance += Math.abs(walk - (this.track.scrollLeft - this.scrollLeft));
        this.track.scrollLeft = this.scrollLeft - walk;

        const now = Date.now();
        const dt = now - this.lastTime;
        if (dt > 0) {
          this.velocity = (touch.pageX - this.lastX) / dt;
        }
        this.lastX = touch.pageX;
        this.lastTime = now;

        if (this.totalDragDistance > this.dragThreshold && e.cancelable) {
          e.preventDefault();
        }
      }

      handleDragEnd() {
        if (!this.isDragging) return;
        
        const wasDragging = this.totalDragDistance > this.dragThreshold;
        this.isDragging = false;
        
        setTimeout(() => {
          this.track.classList.remove('is-dragging');
        }, wasDragging ? 100 : 0);

        if (Math.abs(this.velocity) > 0.1 && wasDragging) {
          this.applyMomentum();
        }
      }

      applyMomentum() {
        const friction = 0.95;
        let currentVelocity = this.velocity * 30;

        const animate = () => {
          if (Math.abs(currentVelocity) > 0.5) {
            this.track.scrollLeft -= currentVelocity;
            currentVelocity *= friction;
            this.animationFrame = requestAnimationFrame(animate);
          }
        };

        animate();
      }

      disconnectedCallback() {
        if (this.animationFrame) {
          cancelAnimationFrame(this.animationFrame);
        }
      }
    }

    customElements.define('luxury-product-carousel-{{ ai_gen_id }}', LuxuryProductCarousel{{ ai_gen_id }});
  })();
</script>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Luxury product carousel",
  "settings": [
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Data source"
    },
    {
      "type": "collection",
      "id": "collection",
      "label": "Collection"
    },
    {
      "type": "product_list",
      "id": "product_list",
      "label": "Manual product list",
      "limit": 24,
      "info": "Used if no collection is selected"
    },
    {
      "type": "range",
      "id": "max_products",
      "label": "Maximum products",
      "min": 4,
      "max": 24,
      "step": 1,
      "default": 12
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Heading"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "heading",
      "label": "Heading",
      "default": "New In"
    },
    {
      "type": "range",
      "id": "heading_size",
      "label": "Size",
      "min": 16,
      "max": 48,
      "step": 2,
      "unit": "px",
      "default": 28
    },
    {
      "type": "select",
      "id": "heading_alignment",
      "label": "Alignment",
      "options": [
        {
          "value": "left",
          "label": "Left"
        },
        {
          "value": "center",
          "label": "Center"
        },
        {
          "value": "right",
          "label": "Right"
        }
      ],
      "default": "center"
    },
    {
      "type": "checkbox",
      "id": "heading_uppercase",
      "label": "Uppercase",
      "default": true
    },
    {
      "type": "color",
      "id": "heading_color",
      "label": "Color",
      "default": "#000000"
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Layout"
    },
    {
      "type": "range",
      "id": "cards_desktop",
      "label": "Cards per view (desktop)",
      "min": 2,
      "max": 5,
      "step": 1,
      "default": 3
    },
    {
      "type": "range",
      "id": "cards_tablet",
      "label": "Cards per view (tablet)",
      "min": 1,
      "max": 4,
      "step": 1,
      "default": 2
    },
    {
      "type": "range",
      "id": "cards_mobile",
      "label": "Cards per view (mobile)",
      "min": 1,
      "max": 2,
      "step": 0.5,
      "default": 1.5
    },
    {
      "type": "range",
      "id": "card_gap",
      "label": "Gap between cards",
      "min": 10,
      "max": 60,
      "step": 5,
      "unit": "px",
      "default": 30
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Product card"
    },
    {
      "type": "select",
      "id": "image_ratio",
      "label": "Image ratio",
      "options": [
        {
          "value": "3/4",
          "label": "Portrait (3:4)"
        },
        {
          "value": "4/5",
          "label": "Portrait (4:5)"
        },
        {
          "value": "1/1",
          "label": "Square (1:1)"
        },
        {
          "value": "4/3",
          "label": "Landscape (4:3)"
        }
      ],
      "default": "3/4"
    },
    {
      "type": "checkbox",
      "id": "show_price",
      "label": "Show price",
      "default": true
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Navigation"
    },
    {
      "type": "checkbox",
      "id": "show_arrows",
      "label": "Show navigation arrows",
      "default": true
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Colors"
    },
    {
      "type": "color",
      "id": "background_color",
      "label": "Background",
      "default": "#ffffff"
    },
    {
      "type": "color",
      "id": "text_color",
      "label": "Text",
      "default": "#000000"
    },
    {
      "type": "color",
      "id": "sale_price_color",
      "label": "Sale price",
      "default": "#d50000"
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Spacing"
    },
    {
